sentences.english: The leader had joined the army much earlier after graduating from high school.

sentences.english: What is more, the author also tries to construct the senior chemistry teaching model of developing autonomous learning.

sentences.english: And then I finished my high school in the U.S.

sentences.english: RESORT】When we were high school students, we resorted to the restaurant.
sentences.chinese: 当我们是高中生时，常去那家餐馆。

sentences.english: For another, there are also some differences between high school life and college school.
